@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin((v2 * (tmp + 0.25 - v2 + 0.35)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.67 + v2 + 0.01)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v1)
    v1 = 0.48
    v2 = ((0.66 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.27)) / wp.cos((v2 + 0.27 / v0 + 0.39)))
    v1 = (v2 - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.52) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
